From e56f44fdc39751168b055a034ebfc90545e5afc2 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Nachiketa Kumar <nachiketa.kumar@intel.com>
Date: Tue, 27 Apr 2021 23:06:26 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] net: Add support for Intel vnic driver

This driver enables a virtual network interface for
intra-soc communication with Programmable Services Engine (PSE)
using Intel Sensor Hub Transport Protocol(ISHTP) on Intel Elkhart Lake
platforms.

v3:
   - Change to ishtp_device_id id table according to commit bf9167a8b40c
("HID: intel-ish-hid: fix module device-id handling")
   - Many coding style fixes and code spell fix
v2:
   - Fixed review comments and rebased
v1:
   - Initial version
	---

Signed-off-by: Nachiketa Kumar <nachiketa.kumar@intel.com>
Signed-off-by: Lili Li <lili.li@intel.com>
---
