 drivers/net/vnic/Makefile    |   6 +
 drivers/net/vnic/eth-ishtp.c | 488 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 5 files changed, 509 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 drivers/net/vnic/Kconfig
